movies.title: Oklahoma City
movies.plot: The bombing of the Alfred P. Murrah Federal Building in Oklahoma City in April 1995 is the worst act of domestic terrorism in American history; this documentary explores how a series of deadly encounters between American citizens and federal law enforcement - including the standoffs at Ruby Ridge and Waco - led to it.
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 Primetime Emmy. Another 2 wins & 1 nomination.
